Class PodcastRemoteItem

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.podcast.PodcastRemoteItem
public class PodcastRemoteItem extends Object
Represents a remote item in a podcast feed that references content hosted on a different feed. This class implements the Podcast Namespace remote-item tag specification, which allows podcast feeds to reference episodes that exist in other feeds, creating a virtual playlist or compilation of content from multiple sources.
